    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and pride of ownership. The exterior finish is vibrant and deep, showing only minor, superficial stone chips on the hood consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the smoke-free cabin is remarkably clean; the upholstery is free of any rips or significant wear, and every button, switch, and digital display functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in great shape, benefiting from a recent professional inspection, a fresh synthetic oil change, and a new battery. The tires have over 70% tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and has been serviced at regular intervals. Included are the original owner\u2019s manuals, a clean title, and a full set of weather-resistant floor mats. This is a well-sorted, dependable car that is ready for immediate delivery.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This expertly maintained automobile represents a premier opportunity for the discerning motorist. Demonstrating a consistent service history and robust mechanical integrity, the vehicle offers a sophisticated and reliable driving experience. The exterior maintains a distinguished presence, complemented by an interior cabin that remains in exemplary order. This selection is intended for those who demand a harmonious balance of proven performance and exceptional long-term value.",
      "price": 36800.0,
