      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a mechanically sound AP2-generation S2000, powered by the iconic F22C1 longitudinal inline-four engine. This unit delivers a linear power band with a high-revving VTEC engagement, mated to a precise 6-speed close-ratio manual transmission. The chassis features the legendary X-bone frame construction and a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring exceptional torsional rigidity and corner-exit traction. All suspension components maintain factory-spec geometry with the signature double-wishbone setup. While displaying minor aesthetic wear consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains robust and the 50/50 weight distribution provides an uncompromised analog driving experience. A well-sorted example for the serious enthusiast.",
